descript.abstract: Street Centerline/Address File for Bernalillo County
descript.purpose: Geocoding and General Reference Street Base Map
descript.supplinf: Most street names come from subdivision plats on file with the Bernalillo County Clerk Address ranges come from the City Zoning Division, the Bernalillo County Zoning Dept and the Village of Los Ranchos Lines are a representation of street centerline and do not necessarily show a calculated street centerline Lines are a representation of filed record data and do not always represent a built roadway
